Definition: This number identifies the Telepass customer. It can be used to merge data between the "Insurance Quotes" and "Transactions" tabs.
This variable takes value 1 if the service belongs to TelepassPay, while it takes value 0 if it belongs to the standard Telepass services (those that use the OBU).
Number of unique transactions in that given year-month-service category
Total expenditures in that given year-month-service category. In Euros.
